room_title: Escape room "Uncle Ned’s Cabin" by Maine Escape Games in South Portland
room_address: 125 John Roberts Rd, Suite 8 South Portland, ME 04106
room_description: Uncle Ned, your favorite family member and an obsessive gadgeteer, has recently passed away. He’s left your inheritance hidden inside his cabin deep within the Maine woods. Now you must figure out how to get inside and find your money before your greedy relatives beat you to it!
